      </trans-unit>
      <trans-unit id="J0O-pt-mNS.text" xml:space="preserve">
        <source>Apple Watch supported firmware version: 6.0 or higher.
Supported IOS version: 13 or higher.

Make sure the application has loaded on your Apple Watch.

Sessions establishing between iPhone and Apple Watch takes some time. Session works short time to save battery.

 You can add extension to your watchface in to corner. Just customize your clockface and find BatteryWatchSK

 If you see:
Sync ❌ - press button 📲Update on your Apple Watch to be Sync ✅

No active widgets👀 - You have no active extension on your watchface. Just add BatteryWatch extension on your watchface.
</source>
